You might be a religious culti primitivist, a utopian, or something
altogether unintere in transhumanity.
.PP
Advantages: +10 Pilot: Spacecraft skill, +10 to a skill of choice, +20
to a Networking: [Field] skill of your choice
.PP
Disadvatages: None
.PP
Common Morphs: All
.SS Criminal
.PP
You are involved with the crime\-oriented underworld.
may work with one of the Sol system's major criminal tions\[em]triads,
the Night Cartel, the ID Crew, Nine Lives, Familae\[em]or one of the
