.SS Extropian
.PP
You are an anarchistic supporter of the free market and private
property.
You oppose government and favor a system where security and legal
matters are handled by private competitors.
Whether you consider yourself an anarcho\-capitalist or a mutualist (a
difference only other Extropians can figure out), you occupy a
middle\-ground between the hypercorps and autonomists, dealing with both
