Common Morphs: Exalts, Olympians, Splicers, Sylphs
.SS Jovian
.PP
Your faction is noted for its authoritarian regime, bio\-conservative
ideologies, and militaristic tendencies.
Where you come from, technology is not to be trusted to everyone and
humans need to be protected from themselves.
To ensure its survival, humanity must be able to defend itself, and
unfettered growth must be checked.
.PP
