.SS Lunar
.PP
You hail from Luna, the original off\-Earth colony world.
Now overpopulated and in decline, Luna is one of the few places where
people still cling to old\-Earth ethnic and national identities.
Your home is also within sight of Earth, a constant reminder that
encourages many \[lq]Loonies\[rq] to be Reclaimers, deploring the
