There is no more want, no more death, no more limits on what you can be.
The scum have immersed themselves in a new way of life, changing
themselves as they see fit, trying out new experiences, and pushing the
boundaries wherever they can ...
and fuck anyone who can't deal with that.
.PP
Advantages: +10 Freefall skill, +10 to a skill of your choice, +20
Networking: Autonomists skill
.PP
Disadvatages: None
.PP
Common Morphs: All
